INSERT INTO wcc.dcp (t, dcpid, category, patbook, content, indexTb) VALUES ('2018-12-13 01:05:24', '49326', '拉觉石杉  Huperzia lajouensis Ching', '西藏植物志第1卷石杉科 Huperziaceae石杉属 Huperzia Bernhardi拉觉石杉 Huperzia lajouensis Ching', '  2. 拉觉石杉
    Huperzia lajouensis Ching, sp. nov. 1)
    Species insignis proxime affinis H. selagini (Linn.) Bernh. var. appressae 
 (Desv.) Ching differt multo minore, 3-6 cm alta, caules singulari vel semel furcati, 4-5 mm diametro (foliis inclusis) foliis laxe imbricatis vel subpatentibus, 3-4 mm longis, 1 mm latis, Linearibus. apice breviter acuminatis vel acutis, textura herbacea, in sicco luteo-viridi, costa distincta dorso applanata (nec carinata). Etiam magis affinis2) H. tibetcae (Ching) Ching, differt multo minore, foliis brevioribus, laxe imbricatis. 
    Xizang; Zayu (Lajou) in muddy pond, alt. 3400 m, C. W. Wang 65861 (typus, HP). 
    这是一个特出的种，与石杉 H. selago (L.) Bernh 相近似，但远较小，高约3-6

厘米，茎单一或二叉，叶为疏松的覆瓦状或近于开展，长3-4毫米，宽约1毫米，短渐尖，草质，中肋明显，背面平坦（不隆起）。也近于西藏石杉 [H. tibetica (Ching) Ching]，不同点在于远较小，叶较短，疏松的覆瓦状排列。
