INSERT INTO wcc.dcp (t, dcpid, category, patbook, content, indexTb) VALUES ('2018-12-13 01:05:37', '49357', '墨脱卷柏  Selaginella medogensis Ching', '西藏植物志第1卷卷柏科 Selaginellaceae卷柏属 Selaginella Spring墨脱卷柏 Selaginella medogensis Ching', '5. 墨脱卷柏 图6: 1-6
    Selaginella medogensis Ching et S. K. Wu, sp. nov. 
    Species heterostachya a turma S. monosporae Spring, sed graciliore, tota planta usque 20 cm alta, foliis minoribus, lateralibus usque 2 mm longis, 1mm basi latis, foliis intermediis apice breviter aristatis costis indistinctis, haud carinatis facile distinguitur. 
    Xizang austro-orient.: Medog, in sylvis alt. 800 m. Qinghai-Xizang Complex Exped. 4375 (typus, HP); Pachak-shiri Distr., Lalung“plastered on the moss cavered bauks in dense mixed forest”alt. 2000-2500 m. F. Ludlow et al. 3723 (Syntypus HP et BM.), 9. V. 1938. 
